cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper is about improving image classification accuracy using position coordinates, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks (cs.LG) and the relationship between parts of objects (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of data augmentation (blurred images) which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
